cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep neural networks and transfer learning, which are topics commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on the analysis and regularization of deep neural networks, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.CV and cs.AI.
